'''2018年环意自行车赛'''是第101届[[环意自行车赛|环意自行车赛]]，于2018年5月4日至27日进行。比赛的起点位于[[以色列|以色列]][[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]，终点位于[[意大利|意大利]][[罗马|罗马]]，除前三个赛段在以色列境内进行外，其他赛段均在意大利境内进行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/giro-ditalia-2018-will-begin-with-jerusalem-individual-time-trial/|title=Giro d'Italia 2018 will begin with Jerusalem individual time trial|website=cyclingnews.com|date=2017-09-17|accessdate=2017-09-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911173753/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/giro-ditalia-2018-will-begin-with-jerusalem-individual-time-trial/|archivedate=2020-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>

总共有来自22支车队的176名运动员参加此次比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/with-spotlight-on-cycling-giro-ditalia-provides-much-needed-break-from-reality/|title=With spotlight on cycling, Giro d'Italia provides much-needed break from reality|publisher=Times of Israel|date=2018-05-05|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180506133201/https://www.timesofisrael.com/with-spotlight-on-cycling-giro-ditalia-provides-much-needed-break-from-reality/|archivedate=2018-05-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终来自天空车队的[[克里斯·弗鲁姆|克里斯·弗鲁姆]]以89小时2分39秒的总成绩夺得此次比赛的总冠军，他凭借此次夺冠，成为历史上首位赢得环意自行车赛总冠军的英国选手以及历史上第七位同时夺得所有[[三大自行車環賽|三大自行車環賽]]总冠军的自行车手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/may/27/chris-froome-wins-giro-ditalia-rome-first-briton-british-winner-cycling|title=Chris Froome wins Giro d'Italia in Rome to join cycling's exclusive club|publisher=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|date=2018-05-27|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180527174606/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/may/27/chris-froome-wins-giro-ditalia-rome-first-briton-british-winner-cycling|archivedate=2018-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。来自太阳网车队的荷兰选手[[汤姆·迪穆兰|汤姆·迪穆兰]]以46秒之差获得亚军，未能成功卫冕<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2018-05-28/chris-froome-takes-historic-giro-ditalia-victory/9806472|title=Chris Froome claims historic Giro d'Italia victory as he completes the Grand Tour triple|publisher=ABC|date=2018-05-28|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528100537/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2018-05-28/chris-froome-takes-historic-giro-ditalia-victory/9806472|archivedate=2018-05-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。来自阿斯塔纳车队的哥伦比亚选手[[Miguel_Ángel_López_(cyclist)|Miguel Ángel López]]在获得总成绩第三的同时也获得了象征最佳青年车手的白衫。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cyclingnews.com/races/giro-ditalia-2018/stage-21/results/|title=Giro d'Italia: Chris Froome takes a third straight Grand Tour victory|website=cyclingnews.com|date=2018-05-27|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703215457/https://www.cyclingnews.com/races/giro-ditalia-2018/stage-21/results/|archivedate=2020-07-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

